de.oaam.model.oaam.restrictions

Interface DeviceRestriction

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA, SignalGroupRestrictionA, SignalRestrictionA, SubfunctionRestrictionA, TaskGroupRestrictionA, TaskRestrictionA, VariantDependentElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeviceRestrictionImpl

    public interface DeviceRestriction
extends TaskRestrictionA, TaskGroupRestrictionA, SignalRestrictionA, SignalGroupRestrictionA, SubfunctionRestrictionA, OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA, ModeDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Device Restriction'. A device restriction forces functions and signals to use or not use a certain device.

    The following features are supported:

    • Device Name
    • Is Forbidden
    • Devices
    See Also:
    RestrictionsPackage.getDeviceRestriction()
